text: MistshenkoanaGorochov AV (1990) In Gorochov [Ed.]. News of systematics and faunistics of Vietnam insects part 1. Trudy Zool. Inst., Akad. Nauk SSSR, Leningrad 209: 20. is a genus of crickets in the subfamily Podoscirtinae and tribe Aphonoidini. Species can be found in tropical southeast Asia through to Australia and western Pacific islands.Orthoptera Species File (Version 5.0/5.0: retrieved 30 August 2019) == Species == Mistshenkoana
